{
  "texts": [
    "Recent studies indicate that nearly 80% of what we perceive as taste is derived from olfactory stimuli, underscoring the necessity of a comprehensive understanding of both sensory systems (Malfeito-Ferreira 2021).",
    "The exploration of olfactory and gustatory mechanisms highlights the complexity of these sensory systems and their biological interactions.",
    "As research in these fields progresses, the demand for advanced analytical tools becomes increasingly apparent.",
    "AI plays a critical role in decoding the intricate networks involved in olfactory and gustatory processing.",
    "AI leverages large datasets to identify patterns, aiding in the understanding of the biological foundations of taste and smell."
  ]
}